titlestmt.titleproper: A Guide to the Rockefeller Foundation records, Treasurer, RG 7 FA117

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on 2024-03-13 12:49:10 -0400.
profiledesc.langusage: Description is written in: English, Latin script.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Records more than 20 years old are open for research. The archival material has been reformatted. Access to the original paper records is restricted. Microfilm user copies are open for research.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Rockefeller Foundation has title, copyright, and literary rights in the collection, in so far as it holds them. Rockefeller Archive Center has authority to grant permission to cite and publish archival material from the collection.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Treasurer's files include but are not limited to: grants, vouchers, cash books, financial reports, payments, appropriations, expenditures, trial balances, and related files.
